OL,3,COverstretched NHS putting cancer
OL,4,Cpatients at risk, ombudsman warns
OL,6,FOther concerns included poor
OL,7,Fcommunication in cancer care, as well
OL,8,Fas referrals, end-of life care and how
OL,9,Forganisations handled complaints.
OL,11,FThe health ombudsman said: "Everyone
OL,12,Fdeserves safe and effective care. But
OL,13,Fpatient safety will always be at risk
OL,14,Fin environments that are understaffed
OL,15,Fand where staff are exhausted and
OL,16,Funder unsustainable pressure."
