OL,4,Cpatients at risk, ombudsman warns
OL,6,FMr Behrens called for "concerted and
OL,7,Fsustained action from government to
OL,8,Fmake sure NHS leaders can prioritise
OL,9,Fthe safety of patients and are
OL,10,Faccountable for doing so".
OL,12,FHe added: "A key part of this is
OL,13,Finvesting in the workforce, for today
OL,14,Fand for the long-term, including
OL,15,Fproviding full funding for the long-
OL,16,Fterm workforce plan."
