OL,3,COverstretched NHS putting cancer
OL,4,Cpatients at risk, ombudsman warns
OL,6,FJohn Eastwood, 79, was left
OL,7,F"disgusted" at the care his wife of 54
OL,8,Fyears Sandra received after going to
OL,9,FYork Hospital with abdominal pain in
OL,10,FJune 2020.
OL,12,FCT scans showed a mass in the
OL,13,Fgrandmother's abdomen, which medics
OL,14,Fput down medication she was taking
OL,15,Ffollowing a heart valve replacement.
