OL,6,F"I feel absolutely disgusted with the
OL,7,F'care' she received from the
OL,8,Fhospital," he added. "They didn't
OL,9,Finvestigate the scan results and just
OL,10,Fput it down to Warfarin straight away.
OL,12,F"It seemed like the medical teams did
OL,13,Fnot communicate with each other and
OL,14,Feverything felt very disjointed. They
OL,15,Fleft her in agony for months before
OL,16,Fshe died."
