OL,6,FMr Behrens added: "What happened to
OL,7,FMrs Eastwood was unacceptable and her
OL,8,Ffamily's grief will no doubt have been
OL,9,Fcompounded by knowing that mistakes
OL,10,Fwere made in her care.
OL,12,F"Her case also shows, in the most
OL,13,Ftragic of ways, that while some
OL,14,Fprogress has been made on my
OL,15,Frecommendations to improve imaging
OL,16,Fservices, it is not enough and more
OL,17,Fmust be done. Government must act now
OL,18,Fto prioritise this issue and protect
OL,19,Fmore patients from harm."
