OL,6,FA spokesperson for York and
OL,7,FScarborough Teaching Hospitals NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust said they "fully
OL,9,Faccept" the ombudsman's findings and
OL,10,Fapologise for the distress caused to
OL,11,FMrs Eastwood and her family.
OL,13,FThey added that the trust has made a
OL,14,Fnumber of improvements and agreed to
OL,15,Fchange its practice following the case.
OL,17,FSir Julian Hartley, chief executive at
OL,18,FNHS Providers, said: "These findings
OL,19,Flay bare the alarming impact of
OL,20,Fstretched resources on patients.
