OL,3,COverstretched NHS putting cancer
OL,4,Cpatients at risk, ombudsman warns
OL,6,F"At a time when demand for services
OL,7,Fhas never been higher, the NHS is
OL,8,Fgrappling with over 110,000 staff
OL,9,Fshortages.
OL,11,F"Trust leaders are doing all they can
OL,12,Fto ensure timely, high-quality care
OL,13,Ffor patients, their number one
OL,14,Fpriority, but their efforts need to be
OL,15,Fbacked nationally.
OL,17,F"The patient ramifications of pared-
OL,18,Fback staff and outdated equipment and
OL,19,FIT systems must not be sidelined."
