OL,6,FSir Julian added that trust leaders
OL,7,Fwelcomed the NHS funding announcements
OL,8,Fin Chancellor Jeremy Hunt's Budget
OL,9,Flast week, but warned that that "deep-
OL,10,Frooted challenges require long-term
OL,11,Fsolutions".
OL,13,F"The government needs to commit to
OL,14,Ffully funding the Long Term Workforce
OL,15,FPlan and secure sustained investment
OL,16,Ffor capital and digital
OL,17,Finfrastructure," he said.
OL,19,F"This way, the NHS will be properly
OL,20,Fequipped to deliver the high-quality
OL,21,Fcare that patients need and deserve."
